'''救主慈悲圣殿'''（{{lang-pl|Sanktuarium Bożego Miłosierdzia}}），或稱'''救主慈悲朝聖地'''，是位於[[波蘭|波蘭]][[克拉科夫|克拉科夫]]市郊{{link-pl|瓦蓋夫尼基 (克拉科夫)|Łagiewniki (Kraków)|瓦蓋夫尼基}}的[[天主教|天主教]][[朝聖地|朝聖地]]及[[宗座聖殿|宗座聖殿]]，係紀念1930年代發生、[[耶穌基督|耶穌基督]]向[[玛利亚·傅天娜·克瓦尔斯卡|傅天娜修女]]的「{{link-en|救主慈悲|Divine Mercy}}」顯現事蹟而設置。

== 簡介 ==
朝聖地內最早興建的設施為{{link-en|仁慈之母女修會|Congregation of the Sisters of Our Lady of Mercy}}所屬的[[修院|修院]]，建于1889-1891年，为[[新哥特式建筑|新哥特式建筑]]。1966年，傅天娜修女的[[圣髑|圣髑]]移入堂内（1993年[[列福|列福]]，2000年[[列圣|列圣]]）<ref name="vatican-1">{{Cite web |url=http://www.vatican.va/holy_father/john_paul_ii/homilies/2002/documents/hf_jp-ii_hom_20020817_shrine-divine-mercy_en.html |title=Vatican website: ''Dedication of the Shrine of Divine Mercy Kraków-Łagiewniki August 2002'' |accessdate=2015-01-26 |archive-date=2011-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111105015109/http://www.vatican.va/holy_father/john_paul_ii/homilies/2002/documents/hf_jp-ii_hom_20020817_shrine-divine-mercy_en.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="vatican-2">{{Cite web |url=http://www.vatican.va/holy_father/john_paul_ii/travels/documents/hf_jp-ii_spe_07061997_sr-faustina_en.html |title=Vatican website: ''Apostolic Journey address by Pope John Paul II at the Shrine, June 7 1997'' |accessdate=2015-01-26 |archive-date=2011-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111110071523/http://www.vatican.va/holy_father/john_paul_ii/travels/documents/hf_jp-ii_spe_07061997_sr-faustina_en.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。提供朝聖者參訪與舉行瞻禮的大殿（主聖堂）則建於1999–2002年，为现代风格建筑，可容纳5000人<ref name="Olsen">''Sacred Places Europe'' by Brad Olsen 2007 ISBN 1-888729-12-0 page 138</ref><ref name="Meera">{{cite book | url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=glrLioBQ3QkC&pg=PA53&dq=%2251.+Basilica+of+Divine+Mercy%22&hl=en&ei=GQ4XTq7iIZLSiAKPpqHSBQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CDAQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=%2251.%20Basilica%20of%20Divine%20Mercy%22&f=false | title=Sacred Travels: 274 Places to Find Joy, Seek Solace, and Learn to Live More Fully | publisher=Adams Media | year=2011 | accessdate=July 9, 2011 | author=Lester Meera | page=53 | isbn=1-4405-2489-0 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121111004429/http://books.google.ca/books?id=glrLioBQ3QkC&pg=PA53&dq=%2251.+Basilica+of+Divine+Mercy%22&hl=en&ei=GQ4XTq7iIZLSiAKPpqHSBQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CDAQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=%2251.%20Basilica%20of%20Divine%20Mercy%22&f=false | archive-date=2012-11-11 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>；旁邊附設高77米的瞭望塔，天氣佳時可眺望克拉科夫市區。

截至2011年，救主慈悲圣殿接待了全世界200万朝圣者<ref name="Meera" /><ref name="Olsen" />。[[若望保祿二世|若望保祿二世]]、[[方濟各_(教宗)|方濟各]]两位教宗分別於1997年和2006年造訪此朝聖地。

